title: Eagles draft, win total breakdown, Flacco/Ben being jerks (Football 05/07)
description:
Jimmy Kempski of PhillyVoice.com joins Will Brinson to talk about the Eagles offseason, including their draft maneuvers, whether they think Carson Wentz will be completely healthy next year, what sort of holes they might have on the roster, what the NFC East is going to look like in 2018, if the Eagles can win 11 games next year and much, much more.
